[8608.117713, "o", "\r\u001b[K \u001b[KESC\b\b\bESC\u001b[KO\bO\u001b[KB\bB\r\u001b[K              replace each sequence of a repeated character that is listed in the last  specified  AR‐\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[7m Manual page tr(1) line 13 (press h for help or q to quit)\u001b[27m\u001b[K"]
